definitions.definition: A file transfer to a given computer or device from a remote one through a network connection .
examples: The download took longer than I expected.

definitions.definition: A file that has been or is intended to be transferred in this way .
examples: I got the download but it wouldn't work on my computer.

main_definition: A file transfer to a given computer or device from a remote one through a network connection .
secondary_definitions: A file that has been or is intended to be transferred in this way .
